CustomField.formula:
IF( OR(
        CONTAINS(TEXT(Type), "Instrument")
       ,CONTAINS(TEXT(Type), "Demo")
       ,CONTAINS(TEXT(Type), "Software")
      )
    ,IF( TEXT(Demo_Samples_run__c) ="", "•Demo/Samples Run;","")
     & IF( AND( SAP_Order__c ="" 
               ,NOT(INCLUDES( Owner.fxUserExtraAttributes__c , "2000-SAP Not Required"))
              ),"•SAP Order #;" ,"")
     & IF( AND( TEXT(Sales_Type__c) = "Service Sales"
               ,Customer_PO__c =""
              ),"•Customer PO;","")        			   
    , ""
  )
/*Since all other fields are needed prior to Closed Won, there should not be any missing fields here.
Also, Closed Reason Detail (Reason_Lost_Detail__c) is LongText and can't be part of a formula, so it is part of V.RULE OPP 071*/
